text: Hein Htet Aung (; born 5 October 2001 ) is a footballer from Myanmar, and a striker for Hanthawaddy United FC. He is a graduate of Myanmar Football Academy. He was named player of the month for the 2020 Myanmar National League September. ==References== ==External Link== *interview *Hein Htet Aung *profile Category:Living people Category:Burmese footballers Category:2001 births Category:Hanthawaddy United F.C. players Category:Association football forwards
